# ── WordPress media: front-domain image paths → the media host ──────────────
# Article bodies hardcode www.startupyeti.com/wp-content/ image URLs, but the
# static Astro site on www doesn't serve /wp-content/ (404). The files live on
# admin.startupyeti.com. One 301 resolves all current + future cases.
/wp-content/*   https://admin.startupyeti.com/wp-content/:splat   301

